<div class='title'>
  <h1 class="title-purp">Another Bad Music Review</h1><br /><br /><br>
  <p>Welcome to Another Bad Music Review! Create a profile so you can leave your music reviews,
    good or bad -- our website doesn't discriminate, but it gives everyone else a chance to!<br>
    That said, make sure to comment on others posts to let them know how you really feel.<br>
    Our site will allow you to learn more about music, provide a safe place for you to share your obsessions, and allow
    you to connect with other music nerds.
    Have fun!
  </p>
</div>

{{#each posts as |post|}}
<div class='row mb-4 post'>
  <div class='col-md-12'>
    {{! Displays the Blog Post's Title --> routes to the blog post when you click on the title }}
    <h2>
      {{! routes to this specific post's page }}
      <a href='/post/{{post.id}}'>
        {{! displays the name of the Post and makes it clickable to that ^ route }}
        {{post.title}}
      </a>
    </h2>
    <div class='col-md-10'>
      <h2>
        <a href='/post/{{post.id}}'></a>
        {{! displays the date it was created and by which user }}
        <p>Posted on
          {{format_date post.date_created}}
          by music snob:<br />
          <a class="snob" href="/user/{{user_id}}">{{user.name}}</a><br>
      </h2>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
{{/each}}


